  | doi =
  | isbn =  0-8133-3725-9
  | page = 552}}
</ref><ref>{{cite book
  | last = Friedrichsmeyer
  | first = E.S.
  | authorlink =
  | coauthors = Tom Lange
  | title = Evidence Dismissed: A Critical Commentary 
  | publisher = Simon & Schuster
  | year = 1997
  | location =
  | pages = 319, 333
  | url =
  | doi =
  | isbn =  0-671-00960-5}}
</ref>  He was hired by the [[Los Angeles Police Department]] to interview Fuhrman in 1981, and the defense later filed his report in the Simpson case.<ref>{{cite news 
  | last = Meier
  | first = Barry
  | coauthors =
  | title = Simpson Lawyers Tell Court They Were Misled on Samples
